<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA74">
<l>eṉṟu morunā ḷoḻiyāmai yāṉirantā</l>
<l>loṉṟu miraṅkā rurukkāṭṭār kuṉṟu</l>
<l>kuṭaiyāka vākātta kōvalaṉār neñcē</l>
<l>puṭaitāṉ peritē puvi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If I beg always, without leaving off a single day,</l>
<l>he won’t feel any compassion, he won’t show [his] form, the cowherd lord</l>
<l>who protected the cows with the hill as umbrella. O heart,</l>
<l>a great place it is, the earth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
